What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Erythroid Maturation Agent Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Erythroid Maturation Agent Market

Global erythroid maturation agent market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the market to account to grow at a CAGR of 6.70% in the above mentioned forecast period.

Erythroid maturation agents are used for the treatment of anemia in adult patients with beta thalassemia who require regular red blood cell transfusions. It is also indicated for the treatment of anemia failing an erythropoiesis stimulating agent. These agents work by regulating red blood cell maturation. Reblozyl is the first and only erythroid maturation agent. It is also known as luspatercept.

Rise in the prevalence of anemia, growing healthcare expenditure, supportive strategies, growing government funding and growing use of the product for different conditions are the factors that will expand the erythroid maturation agent market.

Rise in the research and development activities and surge in the number of clinical trials will provide beneficial opportunities for the erythroid maturation agent market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

However, high cost of medication and side effects of reblozyl such as hypertension, allergic reactions, headache, fatigue, nausea, diarrhea, abdominal pain, blood clots and upper respiratory reactions are the factors that will hinder the market growth and will further challenge the global erythroid maturation agent market in the forecast period mentioned above.

